n":5199,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Sadaqah: Charity is a duty upon every Muslim","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 5, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Musa reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cCharity is a duty upon every Muslim.\u201d They said, \u201cWhat if he has nothing?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cThen he should work with his hands to benefit himself and give in charity.\u201d They said, \u201cWhat if he cannot do\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":943,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/07\/23\/spending-on-your-family-sadaqah\/","url_meta":{"origin":5199,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Sadaqah: Spending on your family is an act of charity","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 23, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Mas'ud reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \"If a Muslim spends on his family seeking reward from Allah, it is charity for him.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 5351, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1002 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi\u00a0(authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0645\u064e\u0633\u0652\u0639\u064f\u0648\u062f\u064d \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0623\u064e\u0646\u0652\u0635\u064e\u0627\u0631\u0650\u064a\u0650\u0651 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":1758,